text: Ðus wæs ðæt land forworht æt Dumaltun ðæ æðelsige forworhte æðelrede cyninge to handa.
Ðæt wæs ðænne ðæt he forstæl æðelwines swin æðelmæres suna ealdermannes.
Ða ridon his men to and tugon ut ðæt spic of æðelsiges huse.
And he oðbærst to wuda, and man hine aflymde ða, and man gerehte æðelrede cyninge ðæt land and æhta.
Ða forgef he ðæt land Hawase his men on ece yrfe.
And Wulfric Wulfrune sunu hit siððan æt him gehwyrfde mid ðam ðe him gecwemre wæs, be ðæs cynges leafe and his witena gewitnesse.
